{"kanda":6,"sarga":63,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तस्यराक्षसराजस्यनिशम्यपरिदेवितम् ।कुम्भकर्णोबभाषेदंवचनंप्रजहास च","trans":"Hearing the lament of the Rakshasa king, Kumbhakarna replied laughing.","words":[{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"राक्षसराजस्य","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"परिदेवितम्","m":"lamentation"},{"d":"निशम्य","m":"hearing"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"इदंवचनम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"बभाषे","m":"replied"},{"d":"प्रजहास च","m":"laughing."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"दृष्टोदोषोहियोऽस्माभिःपुरामन्त्रन्वििर्णये ।हितेष्वनभियुक्तेनसोऽयमासादितस्त्वया","trans":"\"While we were discussing earlier and taking decisions, that disaster foreseen by me has reaped for having not trusted the well wishers.\"","words":[{"d":"पुरा","m":"earlier"},{"d":"मन्त्रन्वििर्णये","m":"while we were discussing and taking decision"},{"d":"अस्माभिः","m":"you"},{"d":"यः","m":"that"},{"d":"दोषः","m":"disaster"},{"d":"दृष्टः","m":"foreseen"},{"d":"सःअयम्","m":"that I"},{"d":"हितेषु","m":"wellwishers"},{"d":"अनभियुक्तेन","m":"not trusted"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"आसादितः","m":"reaped."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"शीघ्रंखल्वभ्युपेतंत्वांफलंपापस्यकर्मणः ।निरयेष्वेवपतनंयथादुष्कृतकर्मणः","trans":"\"Those who do sinful deeds fall unobstructed so also the fruit of your sinful action has come upon you.\"","words":[{"d":"दुष्कृतकर्मणः","m":"those who do sinful deeds"},{"d":"निरयेषु","m":"unobstructed"},{"d":"पतनमेव","m":"fall down"},{"d":"यथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"पापस्य","m":"by the sinful"},{"d":"कर्मणः","m":"action"},{"d":"फलम्","m":"fruit"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"उपेतंखलु","m":"come upon you."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"प्रथमंवैमहाराजकृत्यमेतदचिन्तितम् ।केवलंवीर्यदर्पेणनानुबन्धोविचिन्तितः","trans":"\"O king! All this action was not thought of at the beginning, nor the consequences of action weighed in the pride of your prowess.\"","words":[{"d":"महाराज","m":"king"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"कृत्यम्","m":"action"},{"d":"प्रथमम्","m":"first"},{