":"पञ्चधा","m":"five aspects"},{"d":"योगम्","m":"unites"},{"d":"प्रपश्यति","m":"considering"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"पधिइव","m":"like the path"},{"d":"वर्तते","m":"performs."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"यथागमं च योराजासमयंविचिकीर्षति ।बुध्यतेसचिवान्बध्यासुहृदश्चानुपश्यति","trans":"\"The king who does his duty in time in accordance with justice and thinking intelligently with his ministers, understands rightly.\"","words":[{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"राजा","m":"king"},{"d":"यथागमं च","m":"controlling"},{"d":"समयं","m":"proper time"},{"d":"विचिकीर्षति","m":"in accordance with justice"},{"d":"बुध्या","m":"intelligently"},{"d":"सचिवान्","m":"ministers"},{"d":"बुध्यते","m":"thinking"},{"d":"सुहृदश्च","m":"with friends"},{"d":"अनुपश्यति","m":"understands rightly."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"धर्ममर्थं च कामं च सर्वान्वारक्षसांपते ।भजतेपुरुषःकालेत्रीणिद्वन्द्वानिवापुनः","trans":"\"O Rakshasa king! A man should pursue his duty or worldly gain or sensual pleasures all the three combined or at least any two in time (the scriptures lay down that duty should be pursued in the morning, wealth in the afternoon and sensual pleasures at night).\"","words":[{"d":"रक्षसांपते","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"पुरुषः","m":"man"},{"d":"धर्मम्","m":"duty"},{"d":"अर्थं च","m":"worldly gain"},{"d":"कामं च","m":"sensual pleasures"},{"d":"सर्वान्वा","m":"or all"},{"d":"त्रीणि","m":"three"},{"d":"द्वन्द्वानिवा","m":"at least two"},{"d":"काले","m":"in time"},{"d":"भजते","m":"should pursue."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"त्रिषुचैतेषुयच्छ्रेष्ठंश्रुत्वातन्नावबुध्यते ।राजावाराजमात्रोवाव्यर्थंतस्यबहुश्रुतम्","trans":"\" A sovereign king or a king hearing these three does not recognize the best of the three is in vain even though he heard many.\"","words":[{"d":"राजावा","m":"king or"},{"d":"राजमात्रोवा","m":"equal to king"},{"d":"एतेषु","m":"of these"},{"d":"त्रिषु","m":"three"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that"},{"d":"श्रेष्ठम्","m":"best"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"नावबुध्यते","m":"not recognize it"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"बहु","m":"many"},{"d":"श्रुतम्","m":"heard"},{"d":"व्यर्थम्","m":"is in vain."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"उपप्रदानंसान्त्वं च भेदंकाले च विक्रमम् ।योगं च रक्षसांश्रेष्ठतावुभौ च नयानयौ कालेधर्मार्थकामान्यस्सम्मन्त्ऱ्यसचिवैःसह ।निषेवेतात्मवान्लोके न स व्यसनमाप्नुयात्","trans":"\"You are the foremost of the Rakshasas! After discussing with ministers, a king either by gifting or conciliation or dissension or resorting to all of them at the appropriate time takes resort to pursue virtue, wealth, or sensual pleasures at the right time, never meets with sorrow.\"","words":[{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"श्रेष्ठ","m":"foremost"},{"d":"यः","m":"you are"},{"d":"उपप्रदानम्","m":"gifting"},{"d":"सान्त्वं च","m":"conciliation"},{"d":"भेदं च","m":"dissension"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"तौ","m":"together"},{"d":"नयानयौ","m":"at the appropriate time"},{"d":"काले","m":"right time"},{"d":"धर्मार्थकामान्","m":"virtue, wealth and sensual pleasures"},{"d":"सचिवैःसह","m":"with ministers"},{"d":"सम्मन्त्ऱ्य","m":"discussing"},{"d":"निषेवेत","m":"resorts to"},{"d":"आत्मवान्","m":"self"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"व्यसनम्","m":"sorrow"},{"d":"नाप्नुयात्","m":"not meet."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"उपप्रदानंसान्त्वं च भेदंकाले च विक्रमम् ।योगं च रक्षसांश्रेष्ठतावुभौ च नयानयौ कालेधर्मार्थकामान्यस्सम्मन्त्ऱ्यसचिवैःसह ।निषेवेतात्मवान्लोके न स व्यसनमाप्नुयात्","trans":"\"You are the foremost of the Rakshasas! After discussing with ministers, a king either by gifting or conciliation or dissension or resorting to all of them at the appropriate time takes resort to pursue virtue, wealth, or sensual pleasures at the right time, never meets with sorrow.\"","words":[{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"श्रेष्ठ","m":"foremost"},{"d":"यः","m":"you are"},{"d":"उपप्रदानम्","m":"gifting"},{"d":"सान्त्वं च","m":"conciliation"},{"d":"भेदं च","m":"dissension"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"तौ","m":"together"},{"d":"नयानयौ","m":"at the appropriate time"},{"d":"काले","m":"right time"},{"d":"धर्मार्